{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "training_and_development", "channel": "training_sessions", "user": "mark.smith", "message": "Hi team, I wanted to provide a quick update on our training sessions for the year. As of Q4 2024, we have successfully completed 75% of our training sessions, with a total of 300 participants this year. This is a significant achievement considering the number of new technologies we introduced. Just to note, while these sessions have been crucial for compliance and user training, they don\u2019t directly impact areas like battery management or AI enhancements, which are covered in specialized tech training. Let\u2019s keep up the good work!", "create_at": 1690000000000}}
